{"tid":2016613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美角力】對中國控疫不力失望 特朗普強硬發言：我們可切斷整個中美關係","createTime":"2020-05-14T13:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T06:50:05.000Z","uid":51665,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e398d1767ebcbb340c12a91bac790d002b2ba3ab","tid":2016613,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200514/large/1589462118_4d57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200514%2Flarge%2F1589462118_4d57.jpg&h=3991f12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎觸發中美關係惡化，美國總統特朗普周四接受美國霍士商業頻道訪問，表示對中國控疫不力感到「非常失望」，又指美方對於中國「有很多事情可以做」、「我們可切斷整個（中美）關係」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在訪問中，批評中方處理疫情的手法，稱「他們（中方）根本不應該讓這件事發生。我達成了一個偉大的貿易協議，但現在於我而言已不再一樣。（協議）墨水還未乾，疫情便來了，這令我感到不再一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普指，美方可以與中國切斷關係，說：「現在，你知道如果這樣做會如何？如果切斷整個（中美）關係，可以省下5,000億美元。」<br />\n<br />\n近日中美貿易戰延伸至金融領域，美國聯邦僱員和軍人退休儲蓄計劃委員會正式宣佈，基金將無限期推遲停止投資中國和其他新興市場國家。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200514/QOPDQALRWXF2FE4RBMNIELFE54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200514%2FQOPDQALRWXF2FE4RBMNIELFE54%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7tjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e0f03070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200514%2FQOPDQALRWXF2FE4RBMNIELFE54%2F&h=a0ce38dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200514/QOPDQALRWXF2FE4RBMNIELFE54/</a><br />\n打喇！悶死me喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c4cc13fa1524cc1c78d6f8de76515b68ef9c03","tid":2016613,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"sir this way,  just cut them off"},{"pid":"c2974c058021d27d7bdba3638bb118e5b40ed319","tid":2016613,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"66afe72f546124fdc31a0c129e997881278d542a","tid":2016613,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"斷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a73488e765d9b1c0bc6c7bcaa7e9dfd494955b9","tid":2016613,"uid":52006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"然後同台灣建交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bae8068e9d3800d7ccf7addc8dd4aaf56dab32","tid":2016613,"uid":282149,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"疫情完咗，侵侵連任成功嘅話，大陸一定大撚鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加埋俄羅斯而家俾武漢肺炎跣一鑊咁撚金，雜種仔仲唔撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99451da92da8682ecda6e236055ffa3e517dcc36","tid":2016613,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"係就快，唔好等下個禮拜"},{"pid":"e8965c7aa2c2e0f4f4fa1a0d907e84f75406e49e","tid":2016613,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"無時間啦，快啦"},{"pid":"0196cb9863f436384bf7d2747fc9c02b21bacd98","tid":2016613,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"4b2dede55c0a6a25224f31ec0336580b234f144e","tid":2016613,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"親，快上機到美國去"},{"pid":"57ef0e52b6ca3535e3e7c8b867ec46e3216305bb","tid":2016613,"uid":39777,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"只要同台灣建交，中國就會自動切斷關係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/